<div class="col s12">
  <ul class="collapsible" data-collapsible="accordion">
    <li>
      <div class="collapsible-header profile-header"><span class="badge">자세히 보기</span><i>Hi</i>공유자료실</div>
      <div class="card white darken-1 collapsible-body profile-body">
        <ul class="collection">
          <li class="collection-item">이번학기에 수강하시는 수업의 공유자료실을 빠르게 확인가능 합니다.</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="collection notice-collection">
          <% share_list.each_with_index do |share_unit, index| %>
              <%= link_to share_detail_url(:student => params[:student], :share_unit => share_unit), class: 'collection-item', 'data-turbolinks': false do %>
                  <%= share_unit[5]=='Y' ? '중요 : ' : '' %><%= strip_tags(CGI.unescapeHTML(share_unit[1]).html_safe) %> (조회:<%= share_unit[6] %>)<span class="badge"><%= share_unit[4] %></span>
              <% end %>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>
